				<wikidot:authorName>Mister Ious</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1843963</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Maybe&nbsp;spoilers?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Maybe...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>According to SCP-1000, the Bigfoot civilization came before human civilization. Perhaps the 21st century human Western society is the analog of a part of the Bigfoot society, with humans subconsciously creating things akin to it, unknowingly advancing along the same path as the Bigfoot. It's sort of like how little kids imitate adults, but subconsciously, and if the little kids brutally killed them off.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
